<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10096342>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Pista hataam sp. nov. A. Thoracic region in ventral view. B. Thoracic region in lateral view. C. Thoracic region in dorsal view. D. Fascicle of notochaetae from segment 12. E. Notochaeta from segment 12. F. Uncinus from segment 5. G. Uncinus from segment 6. H. Uncinus from segment 8. I–J. Uncini from segment 11. K. Uncinus from segment 25. Abbreviations, in alphabetical order: Br, Branchia; DLb, Dorsal Lobe; LL, Lateral Lappet; NeP, Neuropodium; NoP, Notopodium; S, Segment; VS, Ventral Shield. Scale bars: A,B,C: 3 mm; D: 0.08 mm; E: 0.05 mm; F–I,K: 0.02 mm; J: 0.03 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10096342/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

